\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1080Gidou_0004]\FFFFF[1012Furea_0005]\N<Guido>...!?

\FX[F]\AA[FFFFF]\MMMMM[jump]\F[1080Gidou_0004]\FFFFF[1012Furea_0012]\N<Flare>At that time, the two of them... used something called

other words, saying you followed them to find the base is a

\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1080Gidou_0000]\FFFFF[1012Furea_0012]\N<Guido>...

\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1080Gidou_0004]\FFFFF[1012Furea_0012]\N<Guido>...Tch. Got found out, huh... Damn it, why didn't those
brats just walk home...

out the information about the base to the BB gang during
that attack...

\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1080Gidou_0001]\FFFFF[1012Furea_0003]\N<Guido>Kukukuku... Aree~, you're quite sharp, aren't you? Flare-
chan (laughs) You weren't so sharp in the past, huh?

\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1080Gidou_Kage]\FFFFF[1012Furea_0003]\N<Guido>Well... now that I've been found out, no need to hide it

accompli with sleeping Flare-chan...

\FX[F]\AA[FFFFF]\F[1012Furea_0009]\FFFFF[2020PureDark_0005]\N<Pure Dark>...Hmmm... Silly♪ You're too kind-hearted, Onee-san. Well,

\FX[F]\AA[F]\M[jump]\F[1012Furea_0011]\FFFFF[2020PureDark_0004]\N<Flare>Initially...? Does that mean, when you were with the Justice

\FX[F]\AA[FFFFF]\MMMMM[no]\F[1012Furea_0011]\FFFFF[2020PureDark_0004]\N<Pure Dark>Yes, I was the research team's guinea pig. You see, despite

\FX[F]\AA[F]\M[jump]\F[1012Furea_0011]\FFFFF[2020PureDark_0004]\N<Flare>...!! G, Guido-san...?

\FX[F]\AA[FFFFF]\F[1012Furea_0011]\FFFFF[2020PureDark_0000]\N<Pure Dark>Hehe, yes, him. Every single day, I was thoroughly violated

\FX[F]\AA[FFFFF]\MMMMM[no]\F[1012Furea_0011]\FFFFF[2020PureDark_0000]\N<Pure Dark>One day, I just couldn't take it anymore. By then, my body

\FX[F]\AA[FFFFF]\F[1012Furea_0011]\FFFFF[2020PureDark_0000]\N<Pure Dark>And then, after fleeing, I was dying because my Lavi ran
